Management and well driller licenses; to amend Sections
29 22-24-1, 22-24-2, 22-24-3, 22-24-4, 22-24-5, 22-24-7, 22-24-8,
30 and 22-24-11 of the Code of Alabama 1975; to further provide
31 for the licensing of well drillers and other persons doing
32 related activity; to increase the fees for licensure and
33 provide a two-year licensure period; to require continuing
34 education of licensees; and to authorize the Environmental
35 Management Commission to adopt rules.
